<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; }
    .steps { background-color: white; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb; }
    .steps ol { margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
    .steps li { margin: 8px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1><%= appName %></h1>
      <p>Welcome to Our Platform!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome, <%= fullName %>!</h2>

      <p>Thank you for signing up for <%= appName %>! Your account has been created successfully.</p>

      <div class="steps">
        <h3>Getting Started:</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Login to your account</strong> using your credentials</li>
          <li><strong>Complete your profile</strong> with additional information</li>
          <li><strong>Explore the dashboard</strong> and familiarize yourself with features</li>
          <li><strong>Configure your preferences</strong> in settings</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= appUrl %>" class="button">Login to Your Account</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Account Details:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Username:</strong> <%= fullName %></li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> Will be displayed on profile</li>
        <li><strong>Account Status:</strong> Active</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Need Help?</h3>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact us at:</p>
      <p>ðŸ“§ <strong><%= supportEmail %></strong></p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        <strong>Security Tips:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
          <li>Always logout when using a shared device</li>
          <li>Use a strong, unique password</li>
          <li>Enable two-factor authentication for extra security</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><%= appName %> - Medical Pharmacy Management System</p>
      <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
